The Prep + Prime Fix+ mist is my go-to product from M.A.C Cosmetics for years now. It is a lightweight mist packed with vitamins and minerals, infused with a blend of green tea, chamomile and cucumber to gently soothe and refresh the skin. It gives an instant boost of hydration. 
I use it before makeup to prime my skin and after makeup to set it. I see a huge difference in the longevity of my makeup and how my skin feels when I include this mist to my routine. 

This season, the brand has launched this cult-favorite product in a 13ML bottle, which is priced at Rs. 750 only. 

Elevate your makeup routine with this lovely spray. Go grab yours!

@MACCosmeticsIndia
#MACFixPlus #MACCosmeticsIndia #AD

Staying hydrated and refreshed this summer with the 100% ultra-hydrating natural mist by @kamaayurveda 💕
Their Pure Rose Water is steam distilled from Kannauj Roses, which instantly hydrates and tones the skin. It also balances the PH levels of the skin for healthy glowing skin. I use it as a toner and as a refresher throughout the day and my skin absolutely loves it!

#kamaayurveda #ad #skincare #rosewater

latestPosts.caption:
Exploring Prague 🤍

We got rains in Prague both days and the temperature dropped enough to get me into pants and a coat lol Didn’t expect cold but somehow it added to the charm. The city is so damn pretty even on a cloudy day 😍 
The Vrtba garden was my favourite. Charming, beautiful and has a fantastic view of the city from the top. Loved it! 

Have you been to Prague? What was the highlight of your trip?
